---++ Mind Map
   * Feature Engineering (Simple)
      

<img src="%ATTACHURLPATH%/FeatureEngineeringSimple.png" alt="FeatureEngineeringSimple.png" width="733" height="408" />

   * Feature Engineering (Complex)


<img src="%ATTACHURLPATH%/FeatureEngineeringComplex.png" alt="FeatureEngineeringComplex.png" width="857" height="532" />

---++ Unreferenced
   * Number of references
   * Lexical features (word prefix)

---++ Orphan
   * Incoming links < 3

---++ Refimprove
   * Number of tokens
   * Ratio: text_length/number_of_references
   * Ratio: sentences/references
---++ Empty Section
   * Number of words in section = 0
   * Number of words in section
---++ Notability
   * In/outlinks
   * Footnotes
   * Tag: proposed deletion (see http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Template:Notability)
   * Number of sections
   * Number of tokens
   * Revision features (age, number of revision etc.)
---++ No footnotes
   * Footnotes = 0
   
---++ Primary Sources
   * Revision features
   * Lexical features(unigrams, bigrams)
   * Number of references
   * Number of different domain references
   
---++ Wikify
   * Number of wikilinks
   * Revision features
   * Ratio: plain_text/markup_text
   * Number of different markup elements (number of sections etc.)
   * Section length
---++ Advert
   * List of ad words
   * Lexical features (unigrams, bigrams)
   * Page parameters (locked page etc.)
   * Last modification by unregistered user?
---++ Original research
   * Revision features
   * Lexical features
   * Number of references
   * Ratio: number_of_references/text_length

-- Main.ArtemVovk - 2012-04-16
  
     
